;padding-top:8px;margin-top:8px;text-align:center;\">请保安核实后放行 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 撕下交保安留存</div></div>\r\n<div style=\"border-top:1px dashed #666;text-align:center;padding:10px 0;font-size:10px;color:#888;margin:0 15px;\">- - - - - - - - - - - - 沿此虚线撕下 - - - - - - - - - - - -</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding:12px 15px;background:#fff;\">\r\n<table style=\"width:100%;font-size:13px;border-collapse:collapse;\">\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;color:#555;width:22%;\">编号</td><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-weight:bold;\">{pass_no}</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;color:#555;\">类型</td><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-weight:bold;\">{pass_type}</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;color:#555;\">业主</td><td style=\"padding:4px 0;\">{owner_name}</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;color:#555;\">房号/车牌</td><td style=\"padding:4px 0;\">{room_number} / {plate_number}</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;color:#555;\">有效期</td><td style=\"padding:4px 0;color:#2e7d32;font-weight:bold;\">{valid_date} {valid_time}</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;color:#555;\">签发</td><td style=\"padding:4px 0;\">{issuer} / {issue_date}</td></tr></table>\r\n<div style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;border-top:1px dashed #ccc;padding-top:8px;margin-top:8px;text-align:center;\">此联交业主留存 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 翠苑新城 物业</div></div></div></body></html>','A5','portrait',5,5,10,10,0,1,9,'2026-06-04 07:16:59','2026-06-04 07:16:59',NULL),(36,'翠苑新城-业主信息登记表','form_CY_ownerinfo','form','<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><style>body{font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\',sans-serif;margin:0;padding:0}</style></head><body>\r\n<div style=\"max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;border:3px solid #4527a0;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;\">\r\n<div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4527a0,#311b92);padding:18px 25px;text-align:center;\">\r\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;color:#fff;letter-spacing:5px;\">业主信息登记表</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);margin-