} &nbsp;|&nbsp; 日期:{bill_date}</div>\r\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:5px 0;color:#666;width:18%;\">交款单位/个人</td><td style=\"padding:5px 0;font-weight:bold;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd;\">{payer_name}</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:5px 0;color:#666;\">房号</td><td style=\"padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd;\">怡丰城 {room_number}</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:5px 0;color:#666;\">电话</td><td style=\"padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd;\">{payer_phone}</td></tr></table>\r\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\r\n<thead><tr style=\"background:#e3f2fd;\">\r\n<th style=\"padding:8px 8px;border:1px solid #bbb;text-align:left;\">收费项目</th>\r\n<th style=\"padding:8px 8px;border:1px solid #bbb;text-align:right;\">数量</th>\r\n<th style=\"padding:8px 8px;border:1px solid #bbb;text-align:right;\">单价(元)</th>\r\n<th style=\"padding:8px 8px;border:1px solid #bbb;text-align:right;\">金额(元)</th></tr></thead><tbody>\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">{fee_item_1}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{fee_qty_1}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{fee_price_1}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{fee_amount_1}</td></tr>\r\n<tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\"><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">{fee_item_2}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{fee_qty_2}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{fee_price_2}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{fee_amount_2}</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">{fee_item_3}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{fee_qty_3}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{fee_price_3}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{fee_amount_3}</td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n<div style=\"background:#e3f2fd;padding:12px 18px;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;\">合计(大写):{amount_cn}</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:bold;color:#e53935;\">¥{total_amount}</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.9;color:#666;margin-bottom:14px;\">\r\n<strong>备注:</strong>{remark}<br><strong>收款方式:</strong>{pay_method} &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>收款人:</strong>{collector}</div>\r\n<div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:12px;margin-top:25px;padding-top:15px;border-top:1px solid #eee;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\"><div style=\"margin-bottom:25px;\">收款单位(盖章)</div><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #333;width:90px;margin:0 auto;\"></div></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\"><div style=\"margin-bottom:25px;\">经手人</div><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #333;width:70px;margin:0 auto;\"></div></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\"><div style=\"margin-bottom:25px;\">交款人</div><div style=\"border-top:1px solid #333;width:70px;margin:0 auto;\"></div></div></div></div>\r\n<div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:8px;text-align:center;font-size:10px;color:#aaa;\">本收据一式两份 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 怡丰城 物业管理处 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 地址:{company_address} &nbsp;|&nbsp; 电话:{service_phone}</div></div></body></html>','A4','portrait',10,10,15,15,0,1,10,'2026-06-04 07:16:59','2026-06-04 07:16:59',NULL),(38,'怡丰城-催缴通知','notice_YF_urge','notice','<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><style>body{font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\',sans-serif;margin:0;padding:0}</style></head><body>\r\n<div style=\"max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;border:3px solid #c62828;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;\">\r\n<div style=\"background:#c62828;padding:18px 25px;text-align:center;\">\r\n<div style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:bold;color:#fff;letter-spacing:5px;\">物业费催缴通知单</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);margin-top:4px;\">怡丰城 物业管理处</div></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding:22px 25px;\">\r\n<div style=\"border-left:3px solid #c62828;padding-left:12px;margin-bottom:18px;\">\r\n<div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#c62828;font-weight:bold;\">催缴编号:{urge_no}</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;\">日期:{urge_date}</div></div>\r\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2.3;margin-bottom:18px;\">\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">尊敬的 <strong>{owner_name}</strong>(房号:<strong>怡丰城 {room_number}</strong>)业主:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">截至 <strong>{cutoff_date}</strong>,您累计欠缴物业相关费用共计 <strong style=\"color:#c62828;font-size:16px;\">¥{total_arrears}</strong>(大写:{arrears_cn}),具体明细如下:</p></div>\r\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\r\n<thead><tr style=\"background:#ffebee;\">\r\n<th style=\"padding:8px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:center;\">序号</th>\r\n<th style=\"padding:8px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:left;\">费用项目</th>\r\n<th style=\"padding:8px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:center;\">欠费期间</th>\r\n<th style=\"padding:8px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">欠费金额(元)</th>\r\n<th style=\"padding:8px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">滞纳金(元)</th></tr></thead><tbody>\r\n<tr><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:center;\">1</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">{arrear_item_1}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:center;\">{arrear_period_1}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{arrear_amount_1}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{late_fee_1}</td></tr>\r\n<tr style=\"background:#fff5f5;\"><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:center;\">2</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;\">{arrear_item_2}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:center;\">{arrear_period_2}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{arrear_amount_2}</td><td style=\"padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ddd;text-align:right;\">{late_fee_2}</td></tr></tbody>\r\n<tfoot><tr style=\"background:#c62828;color:#fff;font-weight:bold;\">\r\n<td style=\"padding:9px 8px;text-align:center;\" colspan=\"3\">合计</td>\r\n<td style=\"padding:9px 8px;text-align:right;font-size:16px;\">¥{total_arrears}</td>\r\n<td style=\"padding:9px 8px;text-align:right;\">¥{total_late_fee}</td></tr></tfoot></table>\r\n<div style=\"background:#fff3e0;border:1px solid #ffcc02;border-radius:6px;padding:14px;margin-bottom:14px;\">\r\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#e65100;margin-bottom:10px;\">重要提示</div>\r\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:2.2;color:#555;\">\r\n1. 请您在收到本通知后 <strong style=\"color:#c62828;\">7日内</strong> 到 怡丰城 物业服务中心结清上述款项。<br>\r\n2. 逾期未缴,滞纳金将按日累计,并可能采取进一步催缴措施。<br>\r\n3. 如已缴纳,请忽略本通知。如有疑问请致电物业服务中心。</div></div>\r\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#555;line-height:2;\">\r\n<strong>缴费地址:</strong>{company_address}<br><strong>联系电话:</strong>{service_phone}<br><strong>收款账户:</strong>{bank_name} {bank_account}</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:right;margin-top:20px;font-size:13px;padding-top:15px;border-top:1px solid #eee;\">\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:4px;\">怡丰城 物业管理处</div><div>{urge_date}</div></div></div></div></body></html>','A4','portrait',10,10,15,15,0,1,10,'2026-06-04 07:16:59','2026-06-04 07:16:59',NULL),(39,'怡丰城-出入放行条','form_YF_gatepass','form','<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><style>body{font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\',sans-serif;margin:0;padding:0}</style></head><body>\r\n<div style=\"max-width:400px;margin:0 auto;border:3px solid #2e7d32;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;background:#f1f8e9;\">\r\n<div style=\"background:#2e7d32;color:#fff;text-align:center;padding:12px 0;\">\r\n<div